<div id="ftn98">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref98" id="_ftn98" name="_ftn98" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference">[98]</span></span></a> UN Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights, “Guiding Principles on Business and Human Rights,” HR/PUB/11/04, adopted June 16, 2011, http://www.ohchr.org/Documents/Publications/GuidingPrinciplesBusinessHR _EN.pdf (accessed December 3, 2019), principle 4.</p>
