<div id="ftn100">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref100" id="_ftn100" name="_ftn100" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference">[100]</span></span></a> Ibid. Article 16.</p>
